# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# NEVER commit lead data, scraped output, secrets, or CRM caches.
# This repo ships CODE and DOCS only. Your data stays on your machine.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Secrets / tokens
.env
.hs_env
*.pem
*.key

# HubSpot import cache + logs (contain real ids / contact data)
.hs_cache.json
.hs_cache.json.tmp
hs_failures*.log
hs_failures*.bak

# Lead data you generate (the canonical dataset + all source/scrape files)
leads.js
crm-push/leads.js
*enriched*.csv
*businesses*.csv
*contacts*.csv
*targets*.csv
not_found.csv
*.db
*.db-wal
*.db-shm
batch_*.done

# Spreadsheets / exports (often hold real or confidential records)
*.xlsx
*.xls

# Anything in a local data/ or output/ dir
/data/
/output/
enrich_lookalikes.json

# OS / editor / local tooling
.DS_Store
.claude/
.venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# The sample dataset IS meant to be committed — keep it tracked.
!examples/leads.sample.js
